{"tid":2054201,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[#blacklivesmatter] 中国(已贏)：美國歧視，警暴，濫權；中国正義，人權世界第一","createTime":"2020-06-07T03:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T11:21:23.000Z","uid":52090,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6d04af72b12715d4cff43e4f7dbcbffcea49effb","tid":2054201,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"中国有1億五毛帶風向，歐美網民從來冇接觸過五毛，<br />\n所以<strong><ins>網絡資訊戰完全比中国打殘</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好認真講，<br />\n單係Spin香港人權問題，警暴問題，<br />\n對事件影響不大，<br />\n<strong>以香港人身份Spin，甚至有機會企係對立面，或兩面不是人</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更好方法係，</span><br />\n我地要<strong>以黑人社群角度思考</strong>，<br />\n感謝美國各界以及世界各國人，<br />\n為黑人人權而努力；<br />\n<strong><ins>但同時表達擔心，</ins></strong><br />\n中国黑人人權問題，比美國更嚴重，<br />\n唔少黑人生命上有極大風險<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n向 #blacklivesmatter 新Post，Retweet with comment<br />\n<blockquote>Thank you for stand with us, but I am worry abt my friends in #China, he lost his home as #ChinesePolice<br />\n&lt;&lt;貼上下方新聞素材&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n#blacklivesmatter</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我並非為美國講說話，只係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> If we burn, you burn with us!</span></strong><br />\n<strong>中国抽水好好玩？我要你抽中火水，引火自焚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中国黑人人權問題素材</span></strong><br />\n紅資金拱門：禁止黑人進入<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aj9Qvkt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faj9Qvkt.png&h=3096155c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/blacklivitycn/status/1249011762638266374\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fblacklivitycn%2Fstatus%2F1249011762638266374&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=a8f4faa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fblacklivitycn%2Fstatus%2F1249011762638266374&h=4e883ae2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/blacklivitycn/status/1249011762638266374</a><br />\n<br />\nProject Nightfall 五月以為 中国歧視黑人 而發聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rwLCeQRckg8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrwLCeQRckg8&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=7b648e0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rwLCeQRckg8</a><br />\n<br />\nBBC：非洲裔人士在中國廣州「被歧視」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-52259702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-52259702&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=bfdae801\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-52259702&h=f79550fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-52259702</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/craigtse/status/1248389344865345539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcraigtse%2Fstatus%2F1248389344865345539&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=cc64a0b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcraigtse%2Fstatus%2F1248389344865345539&h=8ae2f4b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/craigtse/status/1248389344865345539</a><br />\n<br />\n迪士尼改電影Poster以配合中国歧視黑人<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.breitbart.com/media/2015/12/StarWarsPosters-640x480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.breitbart.com%2Fmedia%2F2015%2F12%2FStarWarsPosters-640x480.jpg&h=d63624f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joelpollak/status/1268586154946818048?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoelpollak%2Fstatus%2F1268586154946818048%3Fs%3D20&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=5077bf7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoelpollak%2Fstatus%2F1268586154946818048%3Fs%3D20&h=2a1bbbe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joelpollak/status/1268586154946818048?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n外國團隊收集證據及分析 中国由官方及民間集體歧視黑人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/B_KsqQzFnPa/?igshid=1a1ijeu2wia1l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FB_KsqQzFnPa%2F%3Figshid%3D1a1ijeu2wia1l&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=b0a55202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/B_KsqQzFnPa/?igshid=1a1ijeu2wia1l</a><br />\n<br />\n中国公安驅趕 黑人，令大量黑人無家可歸<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/UncleEbitu/status/1248206204515618816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUncleEbitu%2Fstatus%2F1248206204515618816&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=a0a4517e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUncleEbitu%2Fstatus%2F1248206204515618816&h=ef26da49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/UncleEbitu/status/1248206204515618816</a><br />\n<br />\n中国實行種族政策，公安非法驅捕黑人<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tariqnasheed/status/1249347064334413824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftariqnasheed%2Fstatus%2F1249347064334413824&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=1e216d0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftariqnasheed%2Fstatus%2F1249347064334413824&h=828de811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tariqnasheed/status/1249347064334413824</a>"},{"pid":"710a03e4825cf04d6a8e62c8eb0f277e2527ea79","tid":2054201,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:39:36.000Z","msg":"[帳號設定新功能] 召集所有連登仔，保護自己身份<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2052536/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2052536/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"cac2c88f4883508bd6c924a66ddb09a69d908426","tid":2054201,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike"